      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.526784861
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.526784861
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です、{user}さん……",
      "startTime": 68.1434505104,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "愛、どうしたんだ？　ふらふらじゃないか\nもしかして体調が悪いのか？",
      "startTime": 75.9267896601,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.4009543378
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "い、いえいえ！　どこも悪くなんてありませんよ！\nほら、元気一杯です～……",
      "startTime": 82.5000004451,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.6203904111
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "言ったそばからふらふらしてるじゃないか\n本当になんともないのか？　熱でもあるんじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 88.2648410756,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "なんともありませんから\nほんのちょっぴり、疲れが溜まってる、だけで……",
      "startTime": 94.4666671117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.8680743496
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "お、お仕事中は気合いと根性で乗り切りますから！\n大丈夫ったら大丈夫ですから！",
      "startTime": 103.5000004451,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.967893215
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "……本当に、どうしたんだ？　ちゃんと教えてくれ\nこのままじゃ仕事には行かせられない",
      "startTime": 111.8666671117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.4897982558
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ、分かりました。お仕事が終わったらお話しします\nで、でも、本当に大丈夫ですから、任せて下さい！",
      "startTime": 121.5666671117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "よ～し、今日も頑張りますよ～！\nそれでは、現場に向かいましょう！",
      "startTime": 130.2000004451,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（……仕方ない。愛に無理をさせないよう）\n（俺が気をつけよう）",
      "startTime": 137.3000004451,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.0668008448
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.0668008448
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "……お疲れ様でした\n結局ミスばかりで、本当にすみません……",
      "startTime": 143.9000004451,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "愛、お疲れ様。足を見せてくれ",
      "startTime": 148.6760525665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.3387963416
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！？　{user}さん、こんな所で\nいきなり何言い出すんですか……！？",
      "startTime": 154.7258120419,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "何って、撮影中、セットに向かって派手に転んでただろ\n怪我でもしたんじゃないかと心配だったんだ",
      "startTime": 162.3000004451,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2733.3333332999814,
          "startTime": 165.0333337784
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "……良かった。見た所、痛めてはいないみたいだな",
      "startTime": 166.3146505794,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 166.3146505794
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさい、何もない所で足がもつれちゃって\n大丈夫だって言ったのに……私、ダメダメです",
      "startTime": 175.7666650772,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 181.7874112727
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "愛、何事もなく無事に終わったからいいものの\n怪我をしていた可能性だってあるんだ",
      "startTime": 186.1999984105,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "体調管理も出来てないし、不調の理由も教えてくれない\nこれはプロとして褒められることじゃない",
      "startTime": 193.9333317439,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 196.691833079
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-ai015.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}さんの言う通りです\n本当にごめんなさい。……ちゃんと、お話しします",
      "startTime": 199.5999984105,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
